high_descs: Turn left and walk towards the door, then hang a left and walk over to the round wooden table.
Pick up the egg off of the round wooden table.
Turn right and walk forward, then hang a right and walk over to the fridge.
Open the fridge and put the egg inside, then close the door, after a couple seconds open the fridge and remove the now chilled egg, then close the door.
Turn right and walk over to the round wooden table, then hang a right and walk across the room to the counter.
Place the chilled egg on the counter in front of the apple.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled egg on the counter.

high_descs: Go left and then left again to stand in front of the round table in the corner.
Pick the egg up from the counter.
Turn around and stand in front of the fridge.
Put the egg in the fridge and shut the door and then open the door and take the egg out again and shut the door.
Turn around and cross to face the counter near the microwave.
Put the egg down on the counter in front of the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled egg on the counter.

high_descs: Turn around and walk across the room to face the kitchen table.
Pick up the egg on the kitchen table.
Turn around and walk around to face the front of the fridge.
Cool the egg in the fridge and then remove it.
Turn around and walk forward to face the counter.
Place the egg on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Cool an egg in the fridge plus place it on the counter in front of the microwave.
